-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/daisy-ridley@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/star-wars"><em>《星球大战》</em></a>续集三部曲明星<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/daisy-ridley">黛西·雷德利</a>透露，尽管她领导了这部科幻系列电影，但她并没有“收到很多其他项目的邀请”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/dune-part-2-review-3593580">《沙丘：第二部分》评论：沙虫大小的续集应该会在票房上大吃一惊</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<a href="https://variety.com/2024/film/news/daisy-ridley-star-wars-rey-roles-rise-of-skywalker-1235936745/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Variety</em>报道</a>，上周末，在德克萨斯州奥斯汀举行的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/sxsw-festival"><em>SXSW</em></a>会议上，雷德利讲述了她在<em>《星球大战》</em>续集三部曲的最后一部<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/star-wars-the-rise-of-skywalker-review-2588839"><em>《天行者崛起》</em></a>上映后寻找工作的经历。</p><p>据报道，里德利对出席者说：“并没有那么多的邀请。并不是说没有……我记得我听完后想，‘哦，这里很安静，很奇怪。’” </p><figure id="attachment_2588844" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2588844" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-2588844" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Screenshot-2019-12-18-at-00.36.46.jpg" alt="星球大战 天行者崛起" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Screenshot-2019-12-18-at-00.36.46.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Screenshot-2019-12-18-at-00.36.46-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Screenshot-2019-12-18-at-00.36.46-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Screenshot-2019-12-18-at-00.36.46-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Screenshot-2019-12-18-at-00.36.46-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Screenshot-2019-12-18-at-00.36.46-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-2588844" class="w