en 的</a>伴奏下翻唱吉他独奏。当高斯林在剧院地板上走来走去时，他将麦克风递给<em>芭比</em>导演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/greta-gerwig">格蕾塔·葛韦格</a>、芭比本人、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/margot-robbie">玛格特·罗比</a>和亚美莉卡·费雷拉一起唱歌。高斯林在<em>《爱乐之城》中</em>的搭档<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/emma-stone">艾玛·斯通</a>也加入了进来。 </p><figure id="attachment_3599350" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3599350" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3599350" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/ryan-gosling-slash@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/ryan-gosling-slash@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/ryan-gosling-slash@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/ryan-gosling-slash@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/ryan-gosling-slash@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/ryan-gosling-slash@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/ryan-gosling-slash@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3599350" class="wp-caption-text">瑞恩·高斯林 (Ryan Gosling) 和 Slash 在 2024 年奥斯卡颁奖典礼上表演。图片来源：凯文·温特/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>颁奖典礼早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/finneas">Finneas</a>登台表演<em>芭比</em>剪辑“What Was I Made For”。在高斯林的表演之后，艾利什和芬尼斯凭借同一首歌曲获得了最佳歌曲奖。 </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_91 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_91" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/film/robert-downey-jr-wins-first-oscar-speech-3599274"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p>在 NME.com 上关注 2024 年奥斯卡颁奖典礼的所有动态，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/oscars-2024-winners-full-list-3599250">关注此处公布的获奖者名单</a>。</p></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/ryan-gosling-brings-im-just-ken-to-the-2024-oscars-3599306">瑞恩·高斯林携《I&#39;m Just Ken》参加 2024 年奥斯卡颁奖典礼的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
